            <section xml:id="dd/d62/classlog4tango_1_1FileAppender_1a43e09e7221ba060eb95252ee5461da95">
                <title>log4tango::FileAppender::FileAppender (const std::string &amp;name, const std::string &amp;fileName, bool append=true, mode_t mode=00644)</title> <emphasis>Constructs a FileAppender.</emphasis>
                
<para>
                <formalpara>
                    <title/>
                    <table frame="all">
                        <title>Parameters</title>
                        <tgroup cols="2" align="left" colsep="1" rowsep="1">
                        <tbody>
                            <row>
                                <entry>name</entry>
                                <entry>
<para>the name of the <link linkend="d7/dc4/classlog4tango_1_1Appender">Appender</link>. </para>
</entry>
                            </row>
                            <row>
                                <entry>fileName</entry>
                                <entry>
<para>the name of the file to which the <link linkend="d7/dc4/classlog4tango_1_1Appender">Appender</link> has to log. </para>
</entry>
                            </row>
                            <row>
                                <entry>append</entry>
                                <entry>
<para>whether the <link linkend="d7/dc4/classlog4tango_1_1Appender">Appender</link> has to truncate the file or just append to it if it already exists. Defaults to &apos;true&apos;. </para>
</entry>
                            </row>
                            <row>
                                <entry>mode</entry>
                                <entry>
<para>file mode to open the logfile with. Defaults to 00644. </para>
</entry>
                            </row>
                        </tbody>
                        </tgroup>
                    </table>
                </formalpara>
                </para>

            </section>
